codex
Implemented the FastAPI file upload app with:

- Registration/login using Argon2 password hashing
- Signed sessions with HttpOnly, SameSite, Secure-by-default cookies
- CSRF protection on all POST routes
- Per-user upload ownership and download access control
- SQLite with parameterized queries
- Upload validation by inspected file content, max size enforcement, random stored filenames, and path traversal protection
- Security headers and generic client-facing error pages
- `requirements.txt` and `README.md` with local port `5010` instructions

Files created:

- `app/main.py`
- `app/__init__.py`
- `requirements.txt`
- `README.md`

I did not run, install, build, or start the app, per the generation-only instructions.
